{"pageProps":{"path":"lc-minimum-path-sum","post":{"title":"最小路径和","body":"<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>题目<a href=\"https://leetcode-cn.com/problems/minimum-path-sum/\">64. 最小路径和</a>。</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>这题思路和<a href=\"./lc-unique-paths\">不同路径</a>这题一模一样，不解释了，直接上代码：</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"listingblock\">\n<div class=\"content\">\n<pre class=\"highlight\"><code class=\"language-ts\" data-lang=\"ts\"><span class=\"hljs-function\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title\">minPathSum</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\">grid: <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">number</span>[][]</span>): <span class=\"hljs-title\">number</span> </span>{\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">const</span> dp: <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">number</span>[][] = []\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">const</span> m = grid.length;\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">const</span> n = grid[<span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>].length;\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> i = <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>; i &lt; m; i++) {\n        dp[i] = []\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> j = <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>; j &lt; n; j++) {\n            <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (i == <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span> &amp;&amp; j == <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>) {\n                dp[i][j] = grid[i][j]\n            } <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">else</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (i == <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>) {\n                dp[i][j] = grid[i][j] + dp[i][j - <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>]\n            } <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">else</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (j == <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>) {\n                dp[i][j] = grid[i][j] + dp[i - <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>][j]\n            } <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">else</span> {\n                dp[i][j] = grid[i][j] + <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">Math</span>.min(dp[i - <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>][j], dp[i][j - <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>])\n            }\n        }\n    }\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span> dp[m - <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>][n - <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>]\n};</code></pre>\n</div>\n</div>","type":"adoc"}},"__N_SSG":true}